			<article id="post-759" class="post-759 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-energy-oil-gas tag-christopher-stevens tag-envoy tag-gaddafi tag-iraq tag-islamic tag-jellyfish tag-libya tag-michael-bagley tag-mission tag-movie tag-oil tag-pakistan tag-production tag-security tag-syria tag-tribal tag-yemen">

